The National Working Committee (NWC) of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP), has cancelled its Congresses and their respective Committees in Adamawa, Lagos and Osun States. A statement by  the party’s National Organising Secretary, Abubakar Mustapha, said new committees have been reconstituted accordingly. Mustapha said: “Congresses will continue in these states from Friday, May 6, 2016 respectively.” 